iRepair image assets

This directory holds the renamed marketing and product images used by the app:

- `home-hero-ballpark.jpg` - homepage hero image on `/`
- `about-truck-dusk.jpg` - about page image
- `catalog-bench.jpg` - catalog promo image
- `catalog-bench-alt.jpg` - spare bench variant
- `product-exploded-phone.jpg` - product/detail illustration

The logo lockup lives in `public/brand/irepair-technologies-lockup.jpg`.
